2. Channel Spend vs. Value

Aggregates data to show which ads are working and proves Direct traffic brings in "Big Spenders"

SQL:

SELECT
  channel,
  ROUND(AVG(conversion_value),2) AS avg_conversion_value,
  ROUND(SUM(conversion_value),2) AS total_revenue,
  COUNT(event_type) AS total_purchases
FROM `fluted-box-488519-p3.sql_practice.product_analyst_sql`
WHERE conversion_value > 0 AND event_type = 'purchase'
GROUP BY channel
ORDER BY avg_conversion_value DESC;

- Answer:

Direct is bringing in the Big Spenders, because it has the best Average Conversion Value.

Channel	        avg_conversion_value	      total_revenue	        total_purchases
Direct	            =         263.11	            31310.06	                  119
Google Ads	        =         255.58	            31436.78	                  123
Organic Search	    =         253.79	            30961.79	                  122
Social Media	      =         248.60              28091.77	                  113


